ards]]\n| scope=\"row\"| TV Drama of the Year\n| scope=\"row\"| ''Westworld''\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/2017/01/gay-and-lesbian-critics-association-dorian-award-nominations-galeca-1201768218/ |title=Gay and Lesbian Critics Association Honor 'Moonlight' and 'Jackie' with Dorian Award Noms |last=Dry |first=Jude |date=January 12, 2017 |website=[[IndieWire]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113083128/http://www.indiewire.com/2017/01/gay-and-lesbian-critics-association-dorian-award-nominations-galeca-1201768218/ |archive-date=January 13, 2017 |access-date=January 12, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\"| TV Performance of the Year \u2013 Actress\n| scope=\"row\"| Thandie Newton\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"4\"| [[Motion Picture Sound Editors|Golden Reel Awards]]\n| scope=\"row\"| Best Sound Editing \u2013 Long Form Dialogue and ADR in Television\n| scope=\"row\"| Thomas E. de Gorter, Matthew Sawelson, Brian Armstrong and Fred Paragano (for \"The Bicameral Mind\")\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/motion-picture-sound-editors-golden-reel-award-winners-2017-full-list-winners-970616/item/tv-short-form-dialogue-adr-mpse-golden-reel-winners-2017-976973 |title=Golden Reel Awards: 'Hacksaw Ridge' Tops Feature Competition at Sound Editors' Ceremony |last=Giardina |first=Carolyn |date=February 19, 2017 |website=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170114052433/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/motion-picture-sound-editors-golden-reel-award-winners-2017-full-list-winners-970616/item/tv-short-form-dialogue-adr-mpse-golden-reel-winners-2017-976973 |archive-date=January 14, 2017 |access-date=February 20, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| scope=\"row\"| Best Sound Editing \u2013 Long Form Sound Effects and Foley in Television\n| scope=\"row\"| Thom